data.description: Welcome to Southern living in the heart of Blackshear, GA with this charming, well-maintained home that boasts 5 beds and 3 full baths. Step inside to discover a warm and inviting atmosphere, highlighted by tall ceilings, an open staircase that overlooks the living room, a spacious formal dining room that flows into the beautiful kitchen and breakfast room all showcased by natural lighting flowing in from all the windows. The primary suite is sure to impress with the sitting area/office attached, dual walk-in closets, and the large ensuite bath with dual vanities, walk in shower, and soaker tub! Nestled on a picturesque one-acre lot, this property provides both space and privacy, with a portion of the yard already fenced in, offering a secure area for pets or children to play freely. For those who enjoy outdoor entertaining, there is a grilling area on the back porch adorned with charming pavers, providing the ideal setting for weekend barbecues. A few extra perks are the addition of a Tesla plug and storage shelving in garage, sprinkler system, fiber internet, and transferable termite bond. No HOA! Call today to schedule a showing!
